Instructions for Debugging with Chrome DevTools

1. Open Chrome → Right-click → Inspect

2. Use Elements Tab to change live CSS

3. Open Console Tab to see logs or script errors (console.log() in your script)

4. Use Sources Tab to set JS breakpoints → refresh page → step through execution

5. VS Code → Right-click → "Go to Definition", "Peek Definition", and "Debugger for Chrome" extension can also help debug